channel.title: My DL/UP Speed at School Board :O!
channel.description:
Hey, I'm doing Co-op at my school board (computer technician) and I've done a Speed Test from [code]dslreports.com[/code]... and I just have to say..... WOW.
Here's the pic: [img]http://i.dslr.net/imc/0/0/3/1/46268414.png[/img]
Think I should start dling warez? :twisted: idk if they'd catch me tho :(
I'm here for 3 hours every day, 'nd I could probably bring my external hard drive (400gb) if I want.
